{"id":154722,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/itunes-10强迫用户购买新os-x/","date":"2011-05-23T20:30:50Z","modified":"2011-05-23T20:30:50Z","title":"iTunes 10强迫用户购买新OS X","content":"<p>英国《卫报》报导，iPhone 4或最新一代的iPod shuffle、iPod nano和iPod touch，都需要用户安装iTunes 10才能使用。这似乎没什么大问题，上苹果官网下载即可，但问题是最新版本的iTunes不支持三四年前的旧版本OS X系统。在苹果的支持论坛，有许多顾客抱怨，三年前购买的Mac OS X 10.4.11不能下载iTunes 10，而Windows XP用户却没有这个问题。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/1518b372/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=iTunes+10%E5%BC%BA%E8%BF%AB%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0%E6%96%B0OS+X&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fapple.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F23%2F0726217%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=iTunes+10%E5%BC%BA%E8%BF%AB%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0%E6%96%B0OS+X&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fapple.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F23%2F0726217%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101093631607/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1518b372/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101093631607/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/1518b372/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=NaGCdMr_CJ0:5isfMy02QB0:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=NaGCdMr_CJ0:5isfMy02QB0:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz